<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Ny foko, ry Jehovah ô !
 Fidio ho lapanao ;
 Ekeo ho fonenanao,
 Ka ao no anjakao.

[V2]
 Ny foko, ry Jesosy ô !
 Sasao ho voadio ;
 Izay eritreri-dratsy ao
 Levoninao anio.

[V3]
 Ny foko, ry Fanahy ô !
 Mba hamasinonao ;
 Avia, Fanahy Masina ô !
 Ovay ho fo vaovao.

[V4]
 Ray, Zanaka, Fanahy ô !
 Mpamonjy mahasoa,
 Mpanafaka ahy Hianao,
 Isaorako tokoa.</lyrics>
<title>Ny foko, ry Jehovah o! FFPM610</title>
<author>W. Wheale</author>
<hymn_number>610</hymn_number>
</song>